---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Meet the Team
description: Meet your personal AI team. Six specialists working together to help you navigate life's challenges.
bodyClass: page-team
pageStyles:
  - team-page.css
  - animations.css
---

{# Hero Section #}
<section class="team-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Your AI Team</p>
      <h1 class="headline-xl">Six minds.<br><span class="text-gradient">One purpose.</span></h1>
      <p class="body-lg">Meet the specialists who work together to help you grow.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Team Grid #}
<section class="team-detail-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="team-detail-grid">
      {% for member in site.team %}
      <article class="team-detail-card reveal{% if loop.index > 1 %} reveal-delay-{{ (loop.index - 1) % 3 }}{% endif %}" style="--team-color: {{ member.color }}">
        <div class="team-detail-avatar">
          <span>{{ member.initials }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-detail-content">
          <h2 class="team-detail-name">{{ member.name }}</h2>
          <p class="team-detail-role">{{ member.role }}</p>
          <p class="team-detail-bio">{{ member.bio }}</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Philosophy Section #}
<section class="team-philosophy">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="philosophy-card reveal">
      <h2 class="headline-md">Why a team?</h2>
      <p class="body-lg">
        Real life is complex. No single perspective can cover everything. That's why Ferni brings together 
        specialists who each excel in their domain—from habits to research to life planning.
      </p>
      <p class="body-lg">
        When you talk to one, they seamlessly bring in others when needed. It's like having an entire 
        support team in your pocket, all working together for your growth.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# CTA Section #}
<section class="team-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content reveal">
      <h2 class="headline-lg">Ready to meet your team?</h2>
      <p class="body-lg">Start a conversation today. It's free.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="{{ site.appUrl }}?utm_source=ferni_website&utm_medium=web&utm_campaign=team" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Start Free</a>
        <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneRaw }}" class="btn btn-ghost btn-large">Call {{ site.phone }}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

